These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, soccer, handball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | handball | soccer | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, papaya, onion
1. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | lime | onion | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, camping, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | hiking | camping | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, electronic
1. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | electronic | folk |

