.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby   | hiking | fishing | drawing |

 